title: Nicely updated home located on a large corner lot and within walking~
description: Nicely updated home located on a large corner lot and within walking distance to the elementary school! You will fall in love with this home the minute you drive up. Great curb appeal with lush tropical landscaping welcomes you home. Step inside the spacious Foyer/Entry with custom built in storage area and ''drop'' space. This room has a feature wall with ''wood planks'' giving it a modern country feel. The adjacent Living Room also has a beautiful built in shelf and entertainment center for your flat screen TV. Gorgeous laminate flooring is found in all the main living areas & bedrooms, with tile in the Kitchen, Dining Room & both baths! The Kitchen is light & bright & has been updated with white cabinets, glass tile back splash & a full appliance package! When you want to relax, make you way to the Owner's Suite with it's own private bath. The bathroom features an updated vanity with new countertop, faucet, mirror and a large walk-in shower with custom tile and a frame-less glass door. Two additional bedrooms share an updated guest bath with new fixtures, countertop and a tiled tub surround that goes all the way to the ceiling! The Laundry Room gives you lots of storage space & the washer & dryer are included. Enjoy your morning coffee sitting on the screened porch that is newly renovated. A French door off the Dining Room & Kitchen gives you easy access to this great indoor/outdoor living space! A side door from the screened porch leads down a paver walkway to a large wood deck that is perfect for grilling & entertaining. The yard is fenced in and a double entry gate allows you to fit your RV or boat with ease and there is room for parking 5 cars! This home has it all. Some updates include: Bathrooms & Kitchen updated/remodeled, new tile floors in the Kitchen, Bathroom, & Dining Room areas and Laminate throughout the living areas & Bedrooms, custom built-ins in the entryway & for TV shelving, new interior paint, exterior paint 2015, new Metal Roof 2018, fenced in yard with St. Augustine grass, storage shed, newly renovated patio screen room, lush tropical foliage for privacy, and more! Located only 5 minutes to the river & 10 minutes to the beach! The best part is NO HOA FEE! Make your appt. to see this home today, before it's too late! Email for more details or to set up a viewing: ashleb8950gmailcom

title: Woodspring Suites offers weekly rates starting at $667.
description: NO HASSLE - NO CREDIT CHECKSBefore you decide to stay at Woodspring Suites, we want you to be prepared--prepared for a better experience.  What that means to us is a truly affordable, incredibly clean, safer, simple, flexible experience.  And this is more than just a nice idea --it's the Woodspring Suites promise.  So how do we do it?  By combining all the convenience of a hotel with all the essentials of an apartment.  We are a hybrid--and that makes us better than a hotel, an apartment or any other short-term housing accommodations you’ll find.  Think about it—no extras padded into our price, no hidden fees.   No lease to sign, no utilities to set up.  That’s just for starters.  Find out below more of what to expect when you’re here.•	Clean & Safe –Secure building access with electronically protected interior.  A Safety attendant is available after hotel hours.  All rooms are deep-cleaned after each check-out, and then go through a vigorous multi-point inspection.•	Kitchen— Kitchens have a full-size refrigerator/freezer, ceramic stove-top, microwave, cabinet space and a spacious sink.•	Furnished Studios—Dresser, nightstand, eating table with chair, clothes rack and extra storage space.•	Satellite/Cable – Premium satellite or cable television with Movie Channels•	24-Hour Laundry Facility—On-site laundry facility with keyed guest access only for your safety.•	Linen Exchange— During office hours bring your towels/linens to the front desk for a quick exchange.•	High-Speed Internet—Go online 24/7 with free wi-fi.  High speed internet available for a nominal fee.•	Coffeemaker—A drip coffeemaker that makes 8 to 10 cups.  Yours to keep with a one-time fee.•	Housekeeping –Housekeeping is included every other week.  Additional cleaning can be purchased for a fee.•	Dish Pack—Service for two including plates, bowls, mugs, glasses, utensils, cooking slotted turner, skillet, saucepan, dish cloth and kitchen towel.  Yours to keep for a one-time charge.•	Pets – Dogs are welcome (No Cats).  $50 fee required at check-in plus $10 per night.  Service animals always allowed at no cost.
